                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>N York</placeName>\n                <date>Septembr the 27. 1860</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>The Rev. Leeser</addressee>\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p>Dear Sirâ€”Permit me, respectfully, to recom-<lb/>mend to your kindly notice that I\n                have opened in <placeName>Cha-<lb/>tham Street No. 94</placeName> a Bookstore under\n                the Firm<lb/>\n                <persName>Costez &amp; Guttmann</persName>.</p>\n            <p>In consequence of an unexpected demand for Hebr.<lb/> prayer Mackizim<add>?</add>,\n                chomasiem &amp; Tephiloth we<lb/> have by strong recommendations received<lb/> a\n                depot of every kind from <persName>Frank &amp; Co.</persName>\n                <persName>Ellinger &amp; Co.</persName><lb/>\n                <persName>Rev. Dr. Bondy</persName> etc. in <placeName>N. Y.</placeName> we are glad\n                to<lb/> be able to state that we have sold for the<lb/> Holy days a good\n                    <sic>assortiment</sic>.</p>\n            <p>Now I request also your protection. I live just in the best<lb/> part of\n                    <placeName>N. Y.</placeName> to sell Jewish books. I self was in\n                    <placeName>Holland</placeName><lb/> (whereof I am a native) the Editor &amp;\n                proprietor of<lb/> the Jewish Gazette and publisher of a great many<lb/> works. I\n                request also that you will take informa-<lb/>tion for my person and business to\n                    <persName>Mrs. Frank</persName><lb/>\n                <persName>Rev. Bondy</persName>\n                <persName>Ellinger &amp; Co</persName> and to the <persName>Rev.\n                    Goldsmith</persName><lb/>\n                <sic>wich</sic> Getln send to you his best respects.<lb/> We wish to have in comm.\n                in depot one or two of<lb/> your publications and you will do me a private<lb/>\n                favor to inform yourself about our punctual<lb/> payments. We will send you after\n                selling directly</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3v11w59t/canvas/p1"
                }
